title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter should display in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. Currently, the output parameter is not displaying in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Go to the query result page. 
2. Notice that there is no data being returned. 
3. Open the edit data set dialog and observe that the output parameter is not displayed.
